# Munch-dish

[Munch Dish](http://www.google.com) -> Click to visit site 

An open-source SaaS application built on Nodejs, express and firebase. 

![Markdown Mark](data:image/png;base64,)


that can be integrated to automate all the processes carried out in a restaurant.

___
Processes ranging from
    
>Table Reservation

>Meal Order (Ticketing)

>Payment Automation
